  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7, take your <strong>chicken</strong> out of the fridge, open the packet and let it air, then boil a kettle</p><p>Add the <strong>macaroni</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong>, bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 6-7 min or until cooked with a bite</p><p>Once done, drain the <strong>cooked</strong> <strong>macaroni </strong>reserving a cup of <strong>starchy pasta water</strong> and set aside until later, reserve the pot</p>",
